reviews.review_text: El Paso? I think its Peggy O. I love listening to when the Dead came to Colorado, especially red rocks. McNichols was used as a secondary on red rocks' rainy nights in some cases. One of the good shows when Jerry shines in his late years. Play on. We're listening.
